==English==

====Noun====
'''spod'''
{{wikipedia}}

# (jargon) one who uses [[talker]]s
# (colloquial) one who excessively studies, similar to a [[swot]], but in addition is disliked by fellow students because of it.

=====Quotations=====
*''1993'': E. RAYMOND ''New Hacker's Dict''. (ed. 2) 391 "A true spod..will not talk to someone physically present in the same terminal room until they log onto the same machine that he is using and enter talk mode."

